WEBVTT

00:01.802 --> 00:03.104
Previously on Mom...
Santa Cruz is only

00:03.137 --> 00:05.773
a three hour
and 12 minute drive.

00:05.806 --> 00:08.676
Do you think we should try
the long

00:08.709 --> 00:10.144
I'm game.

00:10.178 --> 00:12.613
Don't I know you from that time
we slept together?

00:12.646 --> 00:15.316
