I-I really got to study.

00:18.286 --> 00:21.055
This isn't just
hooking up anymore.

00:21.089 --> 00:26.127
Cooper, look... I just don't
have the same feelings for you.

00:26.160 --> 00:27.528
I just don't get it, Christy.

00:27.561 --> 00:30.198
I mean, it would be one thing
if there was another guy.

00:30.231 --> 00:31.532
Oh! There is.

00:31.565 --> 00:33.467
There's totally another guy.

00:35.869 --> 00:38.106
I guess I want to be
with the other guy.

00:38.139 --> 00:41.609
Wow, Christy's driving down
to Santa Cruz to see Patrick.

00:41.642 --> 00:44.212
* I'm so excited

00:44.245 --> 00:47.248
