00:53.421 --> 00:55.556
Come on, Bonnie!

00:55.589 --> 00:57.658
This wedding starts at 3:00.

00:57.691 --> 00:59.527
You ready?
Unfortunately,

00:59.560 --> 01:01.729
yes.

01:01.762 --> 01:04.432
Wow. You look...

01:04.465 --> 01:07.301
I know.
"Ho, ho, ho, Green Giant."

01:07.335 --> 01:09.803
How'd you get roped into this?

01:09.837 --> 01:11.605
I made the mistake
of being nice.

01:11.639 --> 01:14.208
Judy's in our meeting. One time
I told her to hang in there.

01:14.242 --> 01:15.809
Next thing I know,
I'm her emergency contact

01:15.843 --> 01:17.645
and a bridesmaid.

01:17.678 --> 01:20.614
Wait a minute. I put on a tie
for a woman you barely know?

01:20.648 --> 01:22.316
You want to trade?

01:23.517 --> 01:25.253
How did Christy get out of this?

01:25.286 --> 01:26.587
Judy hates her.

01:26.620 --> 01:27.821
