led to a fistfight.

01:29.757 --> 01:32.260
Stupid Marjorie broke it up.

01:32.293 --> 01:34.628
Have you seen my pearl earrings?

01:34.662 --> 01:36.797
I've never noticed earrings
in my entire life.

01:38.466 --> 01:40.268
Except for the guy
at my Starbucks.

01:40.301 --> 01:42.470
He's got, like, a piece
of driftwood in there.

01:46.307 --> 01:47.908
Hey, Mom.

01:47.941 --> 01:49.877
Hi. Do you know
where my pearl earrings are?

01:49.910 --> 01:51.579
