what have I done?

03:32.913 --> 03:36.384
Oh, Lucy. Lucy girl.

03:36.417 --> 03:37.651
Christy?

03:37.685 --> 03:39.253
Hi.

03:39.287 --> 03:40.688
:
Hi.

03:40.721 --> 03:42.490
Uh... what are you doing?

03:42.523 --> 03:44.992
