03:45.025 --> 03:47.828
On my roses?

03:49.563 --> 03:50.964
Patrick, I want to be with you.

03:50.998 --> 03:52.800
Well, I want
to be with you, too.

03:52.833 --> 03:54.368
Great.
I'll tell you what.

03:54.402 --> 03:56.437
Um, when you're done,
come on inside.

03:56.470 --> 03:57.805
We'll have a little snack,

03:57.838 --> 04:00.774
