04:29.069 --> 04:31.305
Have you looked
at this schedule?

04:31.339 --> 04:33.907
The service is
an hour and a half.

04:33.941 --> 04:36.977
It's a full Mass with Communion,
a "Blessing of the People."

04:37.010 --> 04:39.380
What the hell is that?

04:39.413 --> 04:41.782
It's when I whisper "Hail,
Satan" under my breath.

04:41.815 --> 04:43.617
