04:43.651 --> 04:45.919
Oh, relax. We'll just
make out in the back row.

04:45.953 --> 04:47.855
Sweetheart,
you're in the ceremony.

04:47.888 --> 04:49.657
Didn't you go to the rehearsal?

04:49.690 --> 04:52.926
Rehearsal?
I'm not hosting SNL.

04:52.960 --> 04:55.663
Hey, when we finally do this,
I say we knock it out

04:55.696 --> 04:57.030
at City Hall, grab some Chinese,

04:57.064 --> 04:59.032
and we're on a plane to Hawaii
by sundown.

04:59.066 --> 05:01.068
See, that is why
I am marrying you.

05:02.836 --> 05:04.972
Some day.

05:05.005 --> 05:07.675
Aw, geez, after the ceremony,

05:07.708 --> 05:09.877
