to the reception?

05:09.910 --> 05:11.812
This better be an open bar.

05:11.845 --> 05:13.881
Yeah, about that...

05:13.914 --> 05:15.916
Hmm, it's a dry wedding.

05:15.949 --> 05:19.086
No alcohol?
Why didn't you tell me?

05:19.119 --> 05:20.654
