kissing anyone but her.

05:44.578 --> 05:47.548
I have been waiting so
long to do this with you.

05:47.581 --> 05:49.450
And by "this,"
I mean...

05:49.483 --> 05:50.884
more than this.

05:50.918 --> 05:53.153
Like a naked
version of this.

05:53.186 --> 05:54.922
Ooh, that sounds fun.

05:58.125 --> 06:00.961
