pillows behind me.

06:16.444 --> 06:19.012
Uh, yeah, well, uh,
my ex-wife is a decorator,

06:19.046 --> 06:21.649
and she's really
into throw pillows.

06:21.682 --> 06:23.016
And art and furniture.

06:23.050 --> 06:26.420
Pretty much everything
in the house that's not me.

06:26.454 --> 06:28.155
Mmm.

06:30.057 --> 06:33.861
So, what you're saying is your
ex-wife is kind of everywhere.

06:36.163 --> 06:39.833
Yeah. I never really
thought about that.

06:39.867 --> 06:42.803
It's just that
it's our first time,

06:42.836 --> 06:44.938
and I want it
to be perfect.

06:44.972 --> 06:46.574
You know what?

06:46.607 --> 06:48.742
I got a surprise
for y now.

06:48.776 --> 06:52.646
How about you and me find
a really nice hotel room?

06:52.680 --> 06:54.848
Oh, my God, hotel sex?

06:54.882 --> 06:57.184
That's the best kind
of sex there is.

06:59.019 --> 07:01.655
I know.
Such a beautiful service.

07:01.689 --> 07:03.591
So moving.

07:03.624 --> 07:05.726
I'll see you at the reception.

07:05.759 --> 07:09.096
Oh, my God, that
was endless.

07:09.129 --> 07:12.466
The standing up,
the sitting down.

07:12.500 --> 07:14.835
That guy walking around
throwing smoke at people.

07:14.868 --> 07:17.471
And if I have to wait
in line for a cracker,

07:17.505 --> 07:20.741
would it kill 'em to spray
a little cheese on it?

07:20.774 --> 07:22.042
I don't know. I thought

07:22.075 --> 07:23.777
