and beat 'em up.

07:27.147 --> 07:29.917
Come on. They were singing
about love in Italian.

07:29.950 --> 07:32.052
Oh, they could have been
singing about linguine.

07:32.085 --> 07:35.022
You don't know.

07:35.055 --> 07:36.524
Are your eyes red?

07:37.925 --> 07:39.793
Please tell me
you weren't crying.

07:39.827 --> 07:42.496
No. Just...
the whole thing got to me

07:42.530 --> 07:44.031
