than I thought it would.

07:44.064 --> 07:46.834
When they took
their two little candles

07:46.867 --> 07:50.203
and lit the one big candle.

07:50.237 --> 07:54.007
They're the one big candle now.

07:54.041 --> 07:56.076
Sorry, I didn't notice.

07:56.109 --> 07:57.845
At that point, I was trying

07:57.878 --> 08:01.849
to slice my Spanx open
with a nail clipper.

08:01.882 --> 08:03.216
Hey, would it be so terrible

08:03.250 --> 08:05.152
if we did the candle thing
at our wedding?

08:05.185 --> 08:06.920
Maybe we even get married
in a church.

08:06.954 --> 08:08.622
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

08:08.656 --> 08:11.024
What happened to City Hall,
Chinese food, Hawaii?

08:11.058 --> 08:14.261
I don't know. Maybe we should
do something more traditional.

08:14.294 --> 08:18.832
The only reason I am not
driving head-on into traffic

08:18.866 --> 08:21.168
is I don't want to
die in this dress.

08:25.272 --> 08:27.207
