09:21.829 --> 09:24.331
No, no, no, no, no.
I get it. I get it.

09:24.364 --> 09:26.900
That second girl
got pretty loud.

09:28.636 --> 09:30.103
So where to now?

09:30.137 --> 09:33.774
Well, I'm gonna take us
to my favorite beach.

09:33.807 --> 09:37.044
It's really secluded
and very romantic.

09:37.077 --> 09:40.681
Oh. The beach.

09:40.714 --> 09:43.383
I think you mean,
"Oh, the beach!"

09:43.416 --> 09:45.052
No, I-I love the beach.

09:45.085 --> 09:47.755
