like English muffins.

09:50.257 --> 09:52.793
We have a lot
of nooks and crannies.

09:56.063 --> 09:57.898
What's going on?

10:00.100 --> 10:02.970
Well,
Christy, um...

10:03.003 --> 10:04.938
