10:04.972 --> 10:07.107
Are you having
second thoughts about this?

10:07.140 --> 10:08.842
What? No.
No, no, no.

10:08.876 --> 10:11.044
It-it's okay,
because i-if you're not

10:11.078 --> 10:13.380
