notches on his belt?

12:42.529 --> 12:45.765
Very interested.

12:49.602 --> 12:51.338
How 'bout this?

12:51.371 --> 12:53.573
We go back to your place,
go to sleep--

12:53.606 --> 12:55.542
and I mean actual sleep--

12:55.575 --> 12:57.878
