in the morning.

12:57.911 --> 12:59.779
I love that idea.

13:06.286 --> 13:08.889
So I'm curious.

13:08.922 --> 13:12.092
What counts as half a notch?

13:15.328 --> 13:17.130
I'm holding firm on my stance.

13:17.164 --> 13:18.899
