for cold, hard cash.

13:51.631 --> 13:53.633
And how 'bout the dollar dance?

13:53.666 --> 13:56.169
You pin money on the bride
to dance with her?

13:56.203 --> 13:58.906
What genius
came up with that idea?

13:58.939 --> 14:01.341
