15:09.642 --> 15:11.678
Lucy, off.

15:11.711 --> 15:14.081
Oh. No, no, no, no, no.
It's-it's okay.

15:14.114 --> 15:16.316
No, it's not okay.
She's on the boys.

15:16.349 --> 15:17.617
Lucy, off.
Come on. Come on.

15:17.650 --> 15:19.486
Attagirl.

15:19.519 --> 15:21.621
Phew. Hey.

15:21.654 --> 15:23.090
How'd you sleep?

15:23.123 --> 15:24.424
Ah.
Huh.

15:24.457 --> 15:26.293
Great. You?

15:26.326 --> 15:28.261
Excellent.

15:28.295 --> 15:30.663
I think we got this part
of the relationship down.

15:30.697 --> 15:34.334
Yes, we have
nailed sleeping.
All right.

15:34.367 --> 15:35.435
Well, you know what?

15:35.468 --> 15:36.970
That settles it then.

15:37.004 --> 15:39.139
We'll be one of those
weird couples who sleeps

15:39.172 --> 15:41.441
